        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Halo <span id="display-name" class="font-bold text-charming-red"></span>! 👋 Mari ukur pemahaman awalmu tentang komunikasi digital yang santun.</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8" id="pretest-container">
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-charming-red">
                <p class="font-semibold mb-4">1. Kato Nan Ampek digunakan untuk...</p>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <label class="block p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100">
                        <input type="radio" name="preq1"> Mempercepat komunikasi
                    </label>
                    <label class="block p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100">
                        <input type="radio" name="preq1" id="pre-q1-correct"> Mengatur kesantunan sesuai konteks dan lawan bicara
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-accent-orange">
                <p class="font-semibold mb-4">2. AREL singkatan dari...</p>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <label class="block p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100">
                        <input type="radio" name="preq2"> Argument, Reason, Example, Learning
                    </label>
                    <label class="block p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100">
                        <input type="radio" name="preq2" id="pre-q2-correct"> Argument, Reason, Example, Link
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-soft-purple">
                <p class="font-semibold mb-4">3. Komunikasi santun penting karena... (Skala 1-5)</p>
                <input type="range" min="1" max="5" value="3" class="w-full" id="pre-q3">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">
                    <span>Sangat Tidak Setuju</span>
                    <span>Sangat Setuju</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button onclick="submitPretest()" class="mt-8 w-full bg-accent-orange text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-600 transition">
            <i class="fas fa-check mr-2"></i>Kirim Jawaban Pre-Test
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- DASHBOARD SECTION -->
<div id="dashboard" class="section container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-charming-red mb-2">Dashboard Belajar</h2>
